SellOfferFront(String, Double, Double, Double, String, String) - Constructor for class com.cs4310.epsilon.nutsinterface.SellOfferFront
SellOfferFront constructor, meant to be used by the frontend; parameters are used to fill all data members that the frontend can determine on its own.
id is set to null by this function, since a real value can only be set by the backend.
expired is set to false, since it is unlikely that a user would want to generate a new offer that's already expired.
offerBirthday is set to the date/time at which the object was made.
